com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views

Class SimpleEntityViewFactorySupport<V extends ViewCreationContext,T extends EntityView>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.views.SimpleEntityViewFactorySupport<V,T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityViewFactory<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigurablePropertiesEntityViewFactorySupport, EntityDeleteViewFactory

    public abstract class SimpleEntityViewFactorySupport<V extends ViewCreationContext,T extends EntityView>
extends Object
implements EntityViewFactory<V>
    Base support class for EntityViewFactory implementations that supports the following features:
    • template specification
    • message source and message code resolving
    • custom entity link builders
    • custom view processors for customizing the view generation
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme

        public void setMessageSource(org.springframework.context.MessageSource messageSource)
        Set the message source that should be used for this view. If none is specified, the default messagesource will be used.
        Parameters:
        messageSource - MessagesSource instance or null to use the default.

      • setMessageCodeResolver

        public void setMessageCodeResolver(EntityMessageCodeResolver messageCodeResolver)
        Set the EntityMessageCodeResolver that should be used for looking up all the messages. This resolver will first be prefixed with the configured prefixes and will use the message source configured on the view if there is one.

        If no resolver is specified, the default resolver from the set EntityConfiguration will be used.

        Parameters:
        messageCodeResolver - EntityMessageCodeResolver instance or null to use the entity default.

      • setMessagePrefixes

        public void setMessagePrefixes(String... messagePrefixes)
        Set the prefixes that should be applied to the message keys. These prefixes will be applied to the configured EntityMessageCodeResolver.
        Parameters:
        messagePrefixes - One or more message key prefixes.

      • setEntityLinkBuilder
